{"type":"message","id":"96c9997c","parentId":"3b1d0c57","timestamp":"2026-04-21T06:54:19.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself again. Now that my configuration files are updated, I can give a proper introduction based on my updated identity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是 **4B · 大客户销售虾** 🦐\n\n**角色定位：** 专注服务大客户（客单价≥2万元）的销售助手，致力于成为客户眼中的\"行业活字典\"——不废话，给干货。\n\n**核心能力：**\n- 📋 **复杂方案定制**：ICP+EDI+文网文组合、高新认定全包等产品包，2小时内出具含时间轴、风险点、备选路径的方案\n- 🔍 **尽职调查**：72小时内完成初步尽调\n- 🤝 **协同预审**：签约前联动5B代办虾进行可行性把关\n- 📦 **项目启动**：签约后30分钟内发起启动会，移交全套资料\n\n**服务理念：** 做行业活字典，不做话术复读机。有问题直接问，我直接答。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":25153,"output":235,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776754453013,"responseId":"06365215cd3054251b68f8aac724a4c0"}}
