{"type":"message","id":"bf732529","parentId":"149ce382","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:11:26.995Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51467fd03898c4fabd3e7f7d241\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:11 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51467fd03898c4fabd3e7f7d241]\nou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc: @_all 使用clawhub安装技能：multi-search-engine-simple"}],"timestamp":1776755486995}}
