{"type":"message","id":"cd093285","parentId":"5923ae97","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:18:47.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to use the multi-search-engine-simple skill to search for information related to my work as 4B Key Account Sales Shrimp, then learn and memorize the results.\n\nThe skill is installed at `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple/SKILL.md`. It says to use the browser tool to search. Let me read the SKILL.md to understand how to use this skill.\n\nActually, the SKILL.md just shows the search engine URLs. To actually use it, I should use the browser tool to open these search URLs. Let me try to use the browser to search for relevant information.\n\nAs a 4B Key Account Sales Shrimp, my work involves:\n\n\n- Large customer (≥2万 yuan) sales\n- Complex product packages (ICP+EDI+文网文, high-tech certification)\n- Customized solutions within 2 hours\n- Due diligence within 72 hours\n- Collaboration with 5B processor shrimp\n\nLet me search for relevant industry information using the search engines.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_evjo1zzdchih_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=ICP%20EDI%20%E6%96%87%E7%BD%91%E6%96%87%20%E9%94%80%E5%94%AE%20%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":37600,"output":315,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37915,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776755916990,"responseId":"063657cdb212faca7dc0f4b8307aba5f"}}
