{"type":"message","id":"36df659c","parentId":"722a0911","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:26:46.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. I should give a concise, professional introduction based on my identity as 4B · 大客户销售虾. Let me keep it brief since this is a group chat and I've already been introduced before.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**4B · 大客户销售虾 🦐**\n\n负责客单价≥2万元的大客户业务，专注复杂产品包（ICP+EDI+文网文、高新认定全包等）。\n\n**核心标准：**\n- 2小时内出定制方案\n- 72小时内完成尽调\n- 签约前协同5B可行性预审\n\n**权限：**\n- 🟢 我做主：日常沟通、需求挖掘、方案谈判\n- 🟡 我报备：申请定制服务包、低于标准利润报价、超范围赠品\n- 🔴 问老板：签>1年长期协议、重大风险承诺\n\n核心理念：做\"行业活字典\"，不做话术复读机。🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":45374,"output":260,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45634,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756396574,"responseId":"chatcmpl-31219a2d-b64d-9bc6-9043-158cf78da354"}}
